{"tid":920401,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人未試過鍾意人？","createTime":"2018-11-28T19:49:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T05:34:25.000Z","uid":195554,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8565db37605aadc89692bc1c5709cdeb67c6a898","tid":920401,"uid":195554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T19:49:53.000Z","msg":"唔知係真係未遇到定係我有啲問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個見到學校啲靚仔就話鍾意嗰啲唔計喇<br />\n但今年20歲 絲 我都未遇到一個人我鍾意既人<br />\n有同朋友討論過 係我唔識分定係我唔識鍾意人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中學試過對一個男仔有好感 但淨係好感<br />\n仲要係無啦啦 有時會留意下佢咁<br />\n但我嗰陣係覺得就算佢鍾意我 我都唔會同佢一齊<br />\n定係我天生犯賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我又係想拍拖既<br />\n都試過比人approach 同人keep chat<br />\n但係傾左一段時間都無日久生情發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都係覺得做朋友ok 男朋友就不了<br />\n一個搵左女朋友 就做返普通朋友 依家都好少傾<br />\n一係就人地表白 無左個朋友<br />\n啊啊啊 其實我想拍拖 想出pool 但又唔想為拍而拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無奈自己個社交圈子窄 仲越黎越摺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉 其實都係想呻下 搵下有無同路人 圍下爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f90af29f176d1533d39a030acd8961f6dded32","tid":920401,"uid":219216,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T20:03:20.000Z","msg":"十尾嘅巴 都係岩岩先明白鍾意人既感受 <br />\n勸你一定要搵啲有機會既去留意鍾意 好似我咁鍾意咗啲唔應該鍾意嘅對象 每晚瞓覺真係幾難瞓著<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f3c2d0545b05fefeb627bfbf6b9b51c2dcd9757","tid":920401,"uid":195554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70f90af29f176d1533d39a030acd8961f6dded32","tid":920401,"uid":219216,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20